It&#8217;s understood three customers were shot inside a tavern near Thohoyandou, resulting in the death of one man. JOHANNESBURG Police are searching for three men who shot and killed a man during a robbery at a tavern outside Thohoyandou over the weekend.It s understood three customers were shot inside the venue after the robbers ordered them to lie on the ground.One man died instantly while the two other victims were seriously wounded.The police s Moatshe Ngoepe says the robbers fled with an undisclosed amount of money. As of now we re still following the suspect, investigating this matter, and we're calling upon all members of the community to contact Colonel William Ramokhubedu. 